page.title: 12County Athletics Meeting
page.content: On Saturday 6th July Jay Lucy and I went to{Carn Brea.Carn Brea}is a place where{Cornish Primary Schools}take their best athletes to compete against other children. We got to{Carn Brea}at half past nine .We had to wait half an hour because it started at 10:00 am. Mr Cooper went to an office where a man told him that he was in charge of the long_jump. Jay was in the second event which was the boys long_jump. The people for the boys long jump were called and Jay went to the pit. Jays best jump was 3 metres and 54 centi_ metres. Lucys event was the girls long_jump which was the 12th event. Lucys best jump was 2 metres and 90 centimetres. My event was the boys 800 metres. Which was the 19th event. I came second to last. My time was 3 minutes and 5 seconds. After my event I went home with my dad.
